trans-unit.source: Provides a way to determine which target controls can be extended by a particular extender control in the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Kan ikke fastslå hvilke mål kontroller kan utvides med en bestemt extender kontroll i verktøykassen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExtenderControlToolboxItem.GetTargetControlTypes%2A> method returns the collection of target types.
The collection is cached for performance by using the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Properties%2A> dictionary.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen er hurtigbufret for ytelsen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Properties%2A>ordlisten.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Properties%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you write an extender control that implements <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl>, but that does not derive from <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>, specify this type in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute> attribute of your control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du skrive en kontroll som extender som implementerer <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl>, men da er ikke avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>, angi denne typen i den <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute>attributtet for kontrollen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute> </xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl>
